<p>A fall campout with Straylight and our kin, in which we come together to
build a temporary village devoted to community, art, music, and creative
self-expression.</p>

<p>Straylight Campout 2017 will be hosted October 7-8 at <a
href="https://goo.gl/maps/pee9ip976582" target="_blank">Gandhara Manazuru</a>, a
beautiful, private, oceanside campsite situated between Odawara and the Izu
Peninsula.</p>

<p>Please fill out this brief questionnaire to complete your registration.</p>

