<p>Straylight Campout 2017は10月7日と8日の2日間に渡って開催されます。伊豆半島の海岸沿いにある、美しくてプライベートなキャンプサイト、<a href="https://goo.gl/maps/pee9ip976582" target="_blank">真鶴ガンダーラ</a>に是非お越しください。</p>

<p>イベントの予約を完了するには、以下の質問にご回答下さい。</p>

<div class="notes">
<p>Notes / 注意事項</p>

<p>Straylight Campout is a small, private event to which you have been specially
invited, and is limited to 80 attendees. Please register as soon as possible.
Registration will close on September 24.</p>

<p>If would like to bring a partner or friend, they must also register
individually through this form, and should have also received an invitation.
Children under 12 are welcome without registration.</p>

<p>Shared meals, including dinner and breakfast, will be prepared with help from
organizers and volunteers (please send a note if you would like to help!), while
drinks will be available at a reasonable price. We encourage everyone to bring
